{"tid":1921403,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"九巴裝通風車窗抗武肺","createTime":"2020-03-12T03:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T11:24:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4da9700bdd46cd62aa0a4be58774646f38217766","tid":1921403,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T03:17:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200312/JHMKRBV3XU4WXWCENG4XD3GJXA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200312%2FJHMKRBV3XU4WXWCENG4XD3GJXA%2F&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=aa35a422\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200312%2FJHMKRBV3XU4WXWCENG4XD3GJXA%2F&h=f2c13fdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200312/JHMKRBV3XU4WXWCENG4XD3GJXA/</a><br />\n<br />\n九巴裝通風車窗抗武肺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200312/large/1583945221_ccab.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200312%2Flarge%2F1583945221_ccab.gif&h=79b1bad7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九巴將為200部巴士加裝橫趟式通風車窗，增加空氣流通。梁志永攝<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情持續，九巴早前指因應客量下跌，削減一成多班次，不少上班族等待巴士的時間增長。九巴傳訊及公共事務部主管林子豪表示，周一開始已加強個別路線繁忙時間班次，承諾繁忙時間內，乘客不會較往常多等超過五分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：輸入個案再傳社區 恐爆第二波疫潮<br />\n<br />\n已按需求加密班次<br />\n<br />\n林子豪表示，留意部份路線客量於繁忙時段有上升，已按需求增加相關路線班次，包括新界西北來往九龍東、港島區長途路線。他提到，乘客乘搭巴士習慣改變，如集中於放工時間回家或假日到郊外遊玩，所以同樣按情況調整班次。他強調，不會出現「乘客想上車，但係上唔到車情況」，如乘客於繁忙時段遇到相關情況，可致電九巴反映。<br />\n<br />\n另外，九巴將為200部雙層巴士，上、下層各加裝兩個橫趟式通風車窗，乘客可選擇開窗，增加空氣流通。車窗通風口長約59厘米，闊16厘米，即長度約為成人手臀。車窗貼有提示，提醒乘客不要將手伸出窗外。來往禾輋及西九龍站的81號巴士線的兩架巴士已改裝，今起投入服務。<br />\n<br />\n他預計半年內完成改裝200多架巴士，並視乎乘客反應，再決定是否在更多車廂內改裝。他續說，車窗參考倫敦等地巴士設計，希望可透過加裝車窗，增加車廂內空氣流動，而運輸署曾派員視察及提供意見，笑言「時代揀咗呢隻窗」。被問到乘客會否因開關窗而增加爭執的機會，他稱相信港人的質素，特別因應疫情，市民更會明白，並疫情結束後，通風窗會鎖上。<br />\n<br />\n■記者李思潁"},{"pid":"664e534c5da94b010aca6b8f583efcca2351d787","tid":1921403,"uid":49245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T03:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好波"},{"pid":"b35dae7ff58b8578ba6179fa196cf6b7a411674f","tid":1921403,"uid":280329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T03:21:30.000Z","msg":"比較想唔好脫班多d"},{"pid":"bc228430bf41130805ba69d961f9eaa4b26429dd","tid":1921403,"uid":293472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T03:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有d司機唔撚開冷氣焗到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6f89f36c9da1c0844c4748dba2c9a8813e3340","tid":1921403,"uid":187957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T03:23:01.000Z","msg":"全部裝晒落鬼車度囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c324a74137b5d46a90309b7ebd42ca794cc6d09","tid":1921403,"uid":91771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T03:40:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.alexander-dennis.com/media/84482/enviro400xlb-18.jpg?center=0.63568773234200748,0.49752475247524752&amp;mode=crop&amp;width=1020&amp;height=600&amp;rnd=131939364590000000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.alexander-dennis.com%2Fmedia%2F84482%2Fenviro400xlb-18.jpg%3Fcenter%3D0.63568773234200748%2C0.49752475247524752%26mode%3Dcrop%26width%3D1020%26height%3D600%26rnd%3D131939364590000000&h=e0c04448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢種窗靚好多"},{"pid":"1937d85cf15b93e66e1dde219044838fb4c1a0f3","tid":1921403,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T03:43:02.000Z","msg":"九巴可否用返可開窗戶的巴士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1903471\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1903471</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"